title: ADC Looking for people to play with
body: Hey NA IGN: Gypsyleeboy Im unranked, haven't played all my provisionals yet, I main adc, but can mid too. My MF and Kalista are really good, we can play some normals if you wanna check me out. But i do want to start playing some ranked soon. Please hit me up in game or here and we can start playing. I have skype, curse, and google hangouts at the moment but i can consider teamspeak or etc if you use it. My name is anthony. Hit me up
